headline: Teradyne Unveils Magnum 7H - The Next-Generation Memory Tester for High Bandwidth Memory Devices
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., August 04, 2025--Teradyne launches Magnum 7H, designed to test high bandwidth memory devices integrated with GPUs and accelerators for generative AI servers.
